As for dirty tricks, I want to hear two things, a 'whizz' when I activate it and a 'whizz' when the thing STICKS.  This would make it much easier to work out what's going on.  It gets resisted a lot, it's only due to the fact you're hitting a lot that it eventually sticks.  I can't keep up with the messages this produces and the whizz sound effects goes off continously.<br>
